name: ENLIGHTENED
description:
In the dark there is not much we can do. It is difficult to determine what the next step should be. Silent and contemplating thinking very deeply. The feeling of fear also came. The body is shaking and the heart is beating fast.

Light is always sought when it is in the dark. Light symbolizes hope. With the light we can see freely around us, without fear and anxiety. We can do anything when the light shines. This is the light of hope that illuminates human life from the gloom of darkness.
